<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Three blocks, in 5 fragments. The first block, which is complete (0.99) has the assembly mark ΕΑ; the second, which is in two fragments (together, 1.67) has the assembly mark <unclear reason="damage">Ϲ</unclear>Α; the third, also in two fragments (together 0.985) has the assembly mark ΖΑ.</p>
</div>
